6TH STREET OASIS
/module text
module image
/image-wrap

module text
Situated on a 2.5 acre property, Curia on the Drag is an urban oasis with a coffee shop that offers local coffee, tea, beer, wine, baked goods, and desserts. Our Food Truck next to the solar pergola features a plant-based menu, and Dad’s Bar offers a selection of beer and wine that you can enjoy anywhere on the property. Book a time to use our free podcast recording studio in partnership with Spotify, or find a quiet place to study or relax with friends.
Curia Coffee & Tea Shop
is open Monday – Friday 7am-9pm, and Saturday – Sunday 9am-9pm
Curia Food Truck
is open every day, 11am-8pm
Dad’s Bar
is open Wednesday – Saturday 3pm-9pm
/module text

module text
We have plenty of first come, first serve seating areas both indoors and outdoors for small meetings and group gatherings, and our beer garden is available to rent for private events. Click the “contact” link at the top of the page for more information.
Keep up to date with our on-site events by checking out our website calendar and following us on Facebook or Instagram.
